import React from 'react';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';

class AddTaskForm extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Container style = {{borderRadius: "20px", marginTop: "100px", backgroundColor: "#F0F0F0", display: "flex", justifyContent: "center", textAlign: "center"}}>
          <Row style = {{paddingTop: "25px", paddingBottom: "25px"}}>
            <Col style = {{padding: 0, height: "40px"}}>
                <Container fluid={true}>
                    <Row>
                        <Col lg = {5} style = {{width: "500px", border: "1px solid black"}}>
                            <Form>
                                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
                                    <Form.Control as="select">
                                        <option>Date</option>
                                        <option>...</option>
                                    </Form.Control>
                                </Form.Group>
                            </Form>

                            <Form>
                                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
                                    <Form.Control as="select">
                                        <option>Month</option>
                                        <option>...</option>
                                    </Form.Control>
                                </Form.Group>
                            </Form>

                            <Form>
                                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
                                    <Form.Control as="select">
                                        <option>Year</option>
                                        <option>...</option>
                                    </Form.Control>
                                </Form.Group>
                            </Form>
                        </Col>
                        <Col lg = {5}>
                            Add Task
                        </Col>
                        <Col lg = {2}>
                            Button
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Container>
            </Col>
          </Row>
      </Container>
);}}

export default AddTaskForm;
